com.orchestranetworks.service

Interface ValidationReportItemSubjectForTable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ValidationReportItemSubject

    public interface ValidationReportItemSubjectForTable
extends ValidationReportItemSubject
    Represents the subject of a validation report item in the context of a table.

    A subject of this type is created using a ConstraintOnTable.

    See Also:
    ValidationReportItem.getSubjectForTable()

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      AdaptationTable getAdaptationTable()
      Returns the table associated with this item.
      RequestResult getRecords()
      Creates and returns an iterator over the records with which this validation item is associated.
      String getXPathPredicateOfRecords()
      Returns the expression specifying the records with which this validation item is associated.

    • Method Detail

      • getAdaptationTable

        AdaptationTable getAdaptationTable()
        Returns the table associated with this item. Table can be null in the following cases:
        • if the containing dataspace has been closed,
        • if the containing dataset has been deleted,
        • if the table no longer exists after a data model refresh.

      • getXPathPredicateOfRecords

        String getXPathPredicateOfRecords()
        Returns the expression specifying the records with which this validation item is associated.
